 sesame seeds for chia seeds.","Keeping the oven door slightly ajar helps to release any moisture and make the mixture as crunchy as possible.<br>","The mix may still be soft after baking, but becomes firm after cooling.","This banana nut crunch is an energetic and gluten-free treat.","Serve with milk or yogurt and fresh fruit or just nibble on its own.<br>"],"basicInfo":["easy","10m","1h","600 g"]}